HEADWORD: Gallican
<hw>Gal"li*can</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>Gallicanus</ets>: cf. F. <ets>gallican</ets>.]</ety> <def>Of or
pertaining to Gaul or France; Gallic; French; <as>as, the
<ex>Gallican</ex> church or clergy</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

