==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Gallican
<hw>Gal"li*can</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>An adherent to, and supporter
of, Gallicanism.</def> <rj><au>Shipley.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

